# DIG

##### get dns from root servers
```
dig +trace www.example.
```

##### get nameserver for a domain
```
dig subdomain.example.com ns
```

##### get nameserver for a domain specifying the nameserver
```
dig @ns2.google.com. google.com ns
```

##### get A (ipv4 ip) for a domain specifying the nameserver
```
dig @ns2.google.com. google.com A
```

##### get AAAA (ipv6 ip) for a domain specifying the nameserver
```
dig @ns2.google.com. google.com AAAA
```

##### get AAAA (ipv6 ip) for a domain specifying the nameserver with a terse answer.
```
dig @ns2.google.com. google.com AAAA +short
```